{
  "stem": "2713.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But me being so young, I maybe didn't take so much notice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was, because I remember always calling names on Jews, you know, and things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Poland, they were very much antisemitic, because I must say that I was afraid more of the Poles then I was afraid of the Germans, because the Germans wouldn't recognize you as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They couldn't say that you are definitely a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Poles, he looked at you, and he could point out, right away, that you were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, but the-- and it was quite big antisemitism in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in '39, as soon as the Germans came in, as they walked into Dzialoszyce, the first thing they did, after a few days, close all the schools for Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no schools for Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is the only thing that I'm missing, because all I could finish was five classes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There wasn't a Jewish school, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Jews were not allowed to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was just, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe as a child, I was happy that I didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember those things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But maybe so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But things started to get, from one day-- worse from one day to the next.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was really just terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, more Germans came into the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we didn't know what to do, because we had the home in Wadowice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had now a home in Dzialoszyce.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the Germans already arrived, my parents decided that my mother and three sisters would go back to Wadowice and look after the home in Wadowice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we would stay here.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
